실연의 애탄을 정말 치료해줄 수 있는 유일한 건.. 시간이야

178
00:00:02,133 --> 00:00:02,200
TED: Okay where were we?

179
00:00:04,501 --> 00:00:04,567
It was June of 2006,

180
00:00:06,334 --> 00:00:06,400
and life had just taken an unexpected turn.

181
00:00:07,968 --> 00:00:08,033
Dad, can't you just skip ahead

182
00:00:09,501 --> 00:00:09,567
to the part where you meet Mom?

