00:01:32,968 --> 00:01:33,033
and Lily's gone and nothing else

221
00:01:34,501 --> 00:01:34,567
even remotely important happened last night,

222
00:01:35,634 --> 00:01:35,701
yeah, I think he knows.

223
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:37,467
Oh, my God.

224
00:01:39,801 --> 00:01:39,868
I-I'm so sorry. Wh--

225
00:01:40,868 --> 00:01:40,934
What happened?

226
00:01:42,801 --> 00:01:42,868
