For the first time, ever,  the three of us are single

237
00:02:04,234 --> 00:02:04,300
at the same time.

238
00:02:06,968 --> 00:02:07,033
I've dreamed about this day, boys,

239
00:02:08,267 --> 00:02:08,334
and it's going to be

